<td style="text-align: center;">莠悟鴻蜊/梧怦/莠牙</td>
<td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></td>
<td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2000-jp/offset/1/page2_limit/1#u-back"><span class="fa fa-times fa-2x"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></a></td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="chat">
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>到达目的地，在那执行给你的程序，训练就算成功。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>首先你要去蜿ｳ髫｣縺ｮ。其他路线比较危险，你可不要乱走。明白了吗，AO-蝗幃峺？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯，明白啦！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>忘记要去哪里了……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>去蜿ｳ髫｣縺ｮ。需要我解释的更详细一点吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>不用！我记住了！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>迷路了……。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>去蜿ｳ髫｣縺ｮ。还明白吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯！我明白啦！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>在哪里哦……。</p>
</div>
