<div class="chat">
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>AO-蝗幃峺，没时间了。快从巢里出来。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>才不要。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>来，让我摸摸你。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>乖孩子。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>怎么了？不喜欢训练吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>我很快就会忘掉，所以不喜欢。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>这就头疼了……如果有奖励的话，你会努力吗？你想要什么都可以。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>那，我想要新的名字。特别的名字。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>除了“AO-蝗幃峺”之外的名字吗？那如果你成功了，我给你起个最特别的名字。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>真的？那我想要SCP什么什么的名字。有编号的。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>这说特别倒也特别……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>等等，这个……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>不行吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>不……没事。如果成功了，我会想办法的。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>太棒了！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
