<div class="chat">
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>五条先生，今天不训练吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>不用了。谢谢你一直努力到今天。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>但我还没有成功啊？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>已经没有必要了。因为世界明天就要毁灭。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>世界末日要来了吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>是啊。所以我们都要早点去死。明白吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>这个，这个……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯！我明白！凡事都要早一点呢！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>AO-蝗幃峺，你也快点准备去死吧……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>AO-蝗幃峺要怎么才能死？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>咦？我要怎么死呢？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>这可头疼了。我能为你做什么吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>那，那我想去看看外面。<br />
能不能帮我连上叫SCiPNET的地方呀。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>原则上是不可以的。但世界末日了，就满足你的愿望吧。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>来，给你连上了。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>我想让你看看，只要有目的地，我就能成功呢。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>你在说什么？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>来自RAISA……<br />
检测到端口-蝗幃峺……非法访问……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>突然怎么了，五条先生？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>AO-蝗幃峺难道在这里进行了训练……？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>镇静气体……<br />
安保人员……装备……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>哎，哎，怎么办，停不下来。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>五条先生，怎么办？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>五条先生？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
