<div class="chat">
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>五条先生，头很疼吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>看上去状态不是很好……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
