</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>看来我今后只能一个人努力了。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>还有我在呢，打起精神来。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>咳，也是。不是垂头丧气的时候。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯嗯。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>对不起，那时做了些奇怪的事情。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>不，你真是帮了我大忙了。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>真的？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>嗯，你做的很不错。<br />
我可以给你之前说好的奖励了。你想要的特别的名字。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>太棒了！是新的巢穴！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>但我有件事想要你帮忙，可以吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>什么事？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>你能去SCiPNET里你喜欢的地方收集信息吗？<br />
然后把信息带回来给我看。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>明白！好的！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
</div>
<table class="bottom">
<tr>
<td style="width: 2%; text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></td>
