</div>
<div class="hole hole9" style="height:140px; width:140px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2000-jp/offset/1/page2_limit/1#u-open9"><img src="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-2000-jp/ana_clear.png" alt="ana_clear.png" class="image" /></a>
<div class="mail">
<blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<blockquote>
<h4><span>来自RAISA的通知</span></h4>
<p>由于检测到SCP-輔s縺阪�，禁止访问本邮件。<br />
需确认详细内容的人员请联系负责人员。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>五条研究员，你那边状况如何？<br />
我这边糟透了。格尼美德协议没能正常解除安全锁。看上去管理员将<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2000">SCP-■縺ｫ帙s</a>给封锁了。靠我一个人对抗基金会最坚固的安全措施，未免太强人所难了。</p>
<p>如果我能早点行动，是不是就能够一切顺利？因为我的过错，人类漫长的历史，很快就要打上句号。<br />
我能做的事只剩下一件。那就是尽快去迎接死亡。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a href="#u-back">关闭</a></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
<div class="hole hole10" style="height:230px; width:230px; left: 50px;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2000-jp/offset/1/page2_limit/1#u-open10"><img src="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-2000-jp/ana_clear.png" alt="ana_clear.png" class="image" /></a>
<div class="area" style="left: -50px; bottom: -70px;">
<table class="top">
<tr>
<td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></td>
<td style="width: 10%;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">莠悟鴻莠/疲怦/晄蜊</td>
<td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></td>
<td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2000-jp/offset/1/page2_limit/1#u-back"><span class="fa fa-times fa-2x"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></a></td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="chat">
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>Clef博士居然也……<br />
谢谢你捡了这些回来。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>我厉害吧。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>厉害厉害，乖孩子。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>我还有件事想要拜托乖孩子，可以吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>好呀，我会努力的！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>我希望你能像训练时那样去SCP-■縺ｫ帙s，然后执行程序。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>如果我成功了，你要摸摸我！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>啊，但我会忘记在什么地方……</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>这次一定没问题的。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>对了，我之前给你的名字你还喜欢吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯！最喜欢了！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>刚刚和你说的SCP-■縺ｫ帙s，也有同样特别的名字呢。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>真的呢。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>你们这下凑一对了。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>那边会有很多人，如果成功了，他们会夸奖你的。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>真的！太棒了！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="you">
<div class="talk youtalk">
<p>这样，就算你忘记了目的地，也能够再次想起来。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
<div class="me">
<div class="talk metalk">
<p>嗯！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
</div>
